## 3. Configuration Files Implemented

### 3.1 TypeScript (`tsconfig.json`)

| Setting | Value | Rationale |
|---------|-------|-----------|
| `strict` | `true` | Per CODEBASE_GOVERNANCE_RULES §3.1 |
| `noUncheckedIndexedAccess` | `true` | Prevents runtime undefined errors |
| `noImplicitOverride` | `true` | Explicit override keyword |
| `noPropertyAccessFromIndexSignature` | `true` | Forces bracket notation |
| `target` | `ES2022` | Modern runtime support |
| `moduleResolution` | `bundler` | Next.js 15 recommended |
| `paths.@/*` | `./src/*` | Path alias configuration |

### 3.2 ESLint (`eslint.config.mjs`)

| Rule Category | Implementation |
|---------------|----------------|
| Base | ESLint recommended + Next.js core-web-vitals |
| TypeScript | `@typescript-eslint/no-explicit-any: error` |
| Imports | Ordered imports with `@/` prefix grouping |
| General | `no-console: warn` (allows warn/error) |

### 3.3 Prettier (`.prettierrc`)

| Setting | Value |
|---------|-------|
| `semi` | `true` |
| `singleQuote` | `true` |
| `tabWidth` | `2` |
| `trailingComma` | `es5` |
| `printWidth` | `100` |
| `plugins` | `prettier-plugin-tailwindcss` |

### 3.4 Tailwind CSS (`tailwind.config.ts`)

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|----------------|
| Dark mode | `class` strategy |
| Content paths | `./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx,mdx}` |
