## 4. Source Files Implemented

### 4.1 `src/app/layout.tsx`

- Root layout with metadata
- Imports `globals.css`
- Minimal, no business logic

### 4.2 `src/app/page.tsx`

- Placeholder home page
- Uses Tailwind classes
- No business logic

### 4.3 `src/app/globals.css`

- Tailwind directives (`@tailwind base/components/utilities`)
- CSS custom properties for theming (ShadCN-ready)
- Light and dark mode variables

### 4.4 `src/lib/utils.ts`

- `cn()` utility function for Tailwind class merging
- Uses `clsx` + `tailwind-merge`

### 4.5 `src/services/apiClient.ts`

- Placeholder file
- Documents that all API calls must go through this client
- Per CODEBASE_ARCHITECTURE_RULES §6.1

### 4.6 `src/types/index.ts`

- Placeholder for global type definitions
- Empty export to prevent module errors

